Michael,<br><br>
Thanks for expressing your feelings. I am there with you. Take Anne's words to heart. She is a good person.<br><br>
I have begun to discover that before I can have a relationship with the world, I have to have a relationship with myself.<br><br>
First, I have to learn to trust.<br><br>
Second, I have to learn to care for myself.<br><br>
Third, I have to learn to like myself.<br><br>
I continue to move in and out of things, and the emptiness is what hurts the most. The emotional pain is constant.<br><br>
I am learning to compensate and control myself.<br><br>
Never forget there are others in this with you. Do not hesitate to go off line on e-mail to me if you need to talk.
